---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Mission">
  <PageHeader
    title="Our Mission"
    subtitle="A congregation devoted to mission and evangelism"
  />

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <blockquote class="font-accent italic text-3xl text-navy mb-4">
          "Go therefore and make disciples of all nations"
        </blockquote>
        <cite class="text-slate">â€” Matthew 28:19</cite>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl text-navy mb-6">Bringing Orthodoxy to Lincolnshire</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg mb-4">
          All Saints of Lincolnshire exists to share the fullness of the Orthodox Christian
          faith with all who seek it. We are a missionary parish, focused on welcoming those
          who have never experienced the ancient Church.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal mb-4">
          Most of our catechumens come to us with little or no church background. We meet
          them where they are, offering patient instruction, warm fellowship, and the
          transforming beauty of Orthodox worship.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl uppercase tracking-wide text-navy mb-4">Evangelism</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-sm">
            We actively reach out to those seeking truth, offering resources, conversations,
            and an open door to experience Orthodox Christianity firsthand. Our livestreamed
            services and Bible studies extend this welcome beyond Lincoln.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl uppercase tracking-wide text-navy mb-4">Catechesis</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-sm">
            Through our catechumenate program and E-Quip sessions, we provide thorough
            instruction in the Orthodox faith for those preparing to enter the Church.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl uppercase tracking-wide text-navy mb-4">Service</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-sm">
            Our faith compels us to serve others. Through our food bank, homeless outreach,
            and prison ministry, we put the Gospel into action in our community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl uppercase tracking-wide text-navy mb-4">Formation</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-sm">
            We are committed to raising up future clergy and lay leaders. Our parish has
            already produced a priest and a deacon, with others in preparation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-navy text-white rounded-xl text-center">
        <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">
          Join Our Mission
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Whether you're exploring Orthodoxy, seeking to deepen your faith, or looking
          to serve others, there's a place for you at All Saints.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/All-Saints/discover" class="btn btn-primary">Discover Orthodoxy</a>
          <a href="/All-Saints/about/ministries" class="btn btn-secondary border-white text-white hover:bg-white/10">Our Ministries</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
